content:
I don't have access to up-to-date information on who the current members of the grammys academy are. however, there are many accomplished musicians who have been members of the academy in the past or are likely to be currently. some examples include:

1. beyoncé
2. taylor swift
3. kendrick lamar
4. adele
5. billie eilish
6. ed sheeran
7. bruno mars
8. lady gaga
9. jay-z
10. pharrell williams
